snippet.title: [Level 1 Stats] Valkyria Chronicles 3 E2 - Extra Missions: The Uninvited Crows - 2 Turns
snippet.description:
Mission Name: The Uninvited Crows
Mission Objectives: Occupy main enemy base camp
Restrictions: None
Grade: ★★★★★
Ace Name: Sugi the Wrong
Ace Drop 1: Alvitr
Ace Drop 2:

This is a DLC mission that is not included in the "E2" version of Valkyria Chronicles 3 and therefore, entirely in Japanese. Translations may not be 100% accurate but it is at least something to go off.
